You&amp;#39;ve committed to optimizing your health, and we&amp;#39;re here to support you every step of the way.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;As part of your 10X journey, we check in regularly to ensure your protocol is aligned with your body&amp;#39;s unique needs and goals. Please take a moment to complete your monthly wellness check-in below.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your answers help us fine tune your plan for optimal results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
1. Have there been any changes to your prescription&amp;#39;s or supplements?&lt;br /&gt;
2. Have you noticed any changes in your body composition?&lt;br /&gt;
3. Are you experiencing any challenges staying on the program?&lt;br /&gt;
4. How many units of Tirzepatide/Semaglutide are you currently injecting?&lt;br /&gt;
5. What is your current goal?&lt;br /&gt;
6. On a scale 1-10, how hungry are you feeling? (10=extremely hungry)&lt;br /&gt;
7.&amp;nbsp;On a scale of 1-10, how string are your cravings? (10=very strong)&lt;br /&gt;
8. What kind of dietary approach are you following? (Carnivore, Keto, Low Carb, Paleo, Intermittent Fasting, Plant-Based, etc)&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
9. How much water are you drinking each day?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
10. How often are you exercising per week?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please rate the following areas of your health, with 1 being the lowest and 10 being the best:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sleep Quality&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Diet Quality&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Energy Level&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Stress Level&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Libido&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Mental Clarity&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Recovery (muscle,stamina,fatigue)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Digestion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Final Question (I promise!)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How can I support you better to help you reach your health goals this month?&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
